          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1613744564623-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Pick a few <strong>leaves</strong> from the <strong>coriander</strong> (save these for garnish!), then chop the rest finely, including the stalks</p><p>Zest the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Roll the<strong> zested lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1613744575785-x200.jpg",
