            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>jackfruit</strong> to a colander and rinse thoroughly with <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Squeeze each piece of jackfruit to remove as much brine as you can</p><p>Add the <strong>rinsed jackfruit</strong> to the middle of a <strong>tea towel </strong>and bring the four corners together to form a ball, twist the ball and squeeze out as much of the liquid as you can</p><p>Chop the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>jackfruit </strong>into small pieces</p>",
